snippet.title: Evo Q (Mario Jams 2) - Release Video
snippet.description:
DOWNLOAD (v1.12):
► https://romhacking.com/hack/evo-q

SOUNDTRACK:
► https://pabloscorner.bandcamp.com/album/evo-q-soundtrack

Surprise, we're back!

A new mod from Team Cornersoft for the Mario Jams 2 competition. A very short, but sweet hack where you explore three levels of the same world, but in a different state and time period. This hack was developed within a week to meet the competition's deadlines.

With this release, we have more hacks that are now back in development, and hopefully we can share progress about those mods soon. Enjoy!

(Note: A clean SM64 ROMs MD5 checksum is "48DE9B252C5740A6CA5BABE6B025EA41", if this matches with your clean ROM, the patch will work with your ROM.)

Credits:
Mel (Modeling)
PablosCorner (Music and Modeling)
Cheezepin (Programming)
Reonu (Optimization)
Wiseguy (Console Testing)

----- TEAM CORNERSOFT -----

Join our discord server!
► https://discord.gg/w3sW6Uh

Want to know more about the team and our projects? Visit our site!: 
► https://teamcornersoft.com/
